com.w2.api.engine.events

Interface RobotEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    W2Event
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GestureEvent, RobotCommandSetSequenceActivity, RobotCommandSetSequenceFinished, RobotCommandSetSequenceStopped, RobotConnected, RobotConnectionEvent, RobotConnectionFailed, RobotDisconnected, RobotLost, RobotSensorSetUpdated

    public interface RobotEvent
extends W2Event
    An interface for all events related to a specific Robot. This interface ensures there is a method for getting a reference to the robot for which the event occurred and should only represent events for connected robots.

    Events for non-connected or discovered robots will implement RobotDeviceEvent.
